>
	<p>
		Zuzi Knaze is an interior creator based in The Hague, working at the intersection of
		architecture, spatial design, and everyday life.
	</p>

	<p>
		Every project starts with careful listening — to the space, to the people who inhabit it,
		and to the light that moves through it. The result is always honest and personal: spaces
		that feel both considered and lived-in, where beauty grows from function rather than
		sitting on top of it.
	</p>

	<p>
		Zuzi works on residential and small commercial projects, from full renovations to custom
		furniture and focused consultations. Sustainability and natural materials guide each
		decision — not as a trend, but as a way of thinking.
	</p>

	<p>
		Every commission is an opportunity to create something creative, meaningful, and lasting.
	</p>
</Layout>
